<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Lightweight_markup_language&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4" title="Edit section: Data serialization oriented">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Data serialization oriented</span></h3>
